SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Amount], [t].[AmountSuppliers], [t].[Carsher], [t].[Code], [t].[Comid], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[CreatedBy], [t].[CreatedOn], [t].[DebtAmount], [t].[DisCount], [t].[DisCountAmount], [t].[IdInvoice], [t].[IdPayment], [t].[IdSuppliers], [t].[LastModifiedBy], [t].[LastModifiedOn], [t].[Note], [t].[PurchaseNo], [t].[PurchaseOrderCode], [t].[Quantity], [t].[Status], [t].[SuppliersCode], [t].[SuppliersName], [t].[Total], [t].[Type], [s].[Id], [s].[Address], [s].[Amount], [s].[CodeSupplier], [s].[ComId], [s].[CreatedBy], [s].[CreatedOn], [s].[Email], [s].[IdCity], [s].[IdDistrict], [s].[LastModifiedBy], [s].[LastModifiedOn], [s].[Name], [s].[Note], [s].[Phonenumber], [s].[Slug], [s].[TaxCode]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Amount], [p].[AmountSuppliers], [p].[Carsher], [p].[Code], [p].[Comid], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[CreatedBy], [p].[CreatedOn], [p].[DebtAmount], [p].[DisCount], [p].[DisCountAmount], [p].[IdInvoice], [p].[IdPayment], [p].[IdSuppliers], [p].[LastModifiedBy], [p].[LastModifiedOn], [p].[Note], [p].[PurchaseNo], [p].[PurchaseOrderCode], [p].[Quantity], [p].[Status], [p].[SuppliersCode], [p].[SuppliersName], [p].[Total], [p].[Type]
    FROM [PurchaseOrder] AS [p]
    WHERE ([p].[Comid] = @__ComId_0) AND ([p].[Type] = @__Type_1)
    ORDER BY [p].[Id] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [Suppliers] AS [s] ON [t].[IdSuppliers] = [s].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id] DESC
